08:27.694 --> 08:29.530
JUST HE'S CRAZY, CANDACE.

08:32.866 --> 08:35.035
THIS IS GOOD.

08:35.035 --> 08:36.302
NO, IT'S NOT GOOD.

08:37.370 --> 08:38.639
YES, IT IS.

08:43.043 --> 08:44.745
WHAT?
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

08:46.813 --> 08:47.981
WE CAN USE THIS.

08:50.016 --> 08:51.518
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

08:51.518 --> 08:52.686
GET YOUR HEAD
IN THE GAME.

08:54.521 --> 08:56.489
THIS IS OUR FREEDOM,
JEFFERY.

08:56.489 --> 08:57.490
NO.

08:57.490 --> 09:00.661
YOU ARE GOING
TO HAVE TO PLAY THIS THING

09:00.661 --> 09:02.969
