CAN I GET A RIDE?

14:34.668 --> 14:35.669
HELL NO.

14:35.669 --> 14:36.737
MAN.

14:36.737 --> 14:37.838
DRIVER, I'M READY.

14:51.351 --> 14:52.485
YES?

14:52.485 --> 14:54.287
HAS MY WIFE BEEN PROCESSED
AND RELEASED?

14:54.287 --> 14:55.155
WHO'S YOUR WIFE?

14:55.155 --> 14:56.156
VERONICA HARRINGTON.

14:56.156 --> 14:58.158
YES.
HOW LONG AGO?

14:58.158 --> 14:59.726
UH, 30 MINUTES,
AN HOUR.

14:59.726 --> 15:01.568
WE GET A LOT OF PEOPLE
THROUGH HERE, SIR.

15:01.568 --> 15:03.036
I'D LIKE TO SEE
JIM CRYER.

15:03.036 --> 15:03.904
AND WHO ARE YOU?

15:03.904 --> 15:05.639
JUDGE DAVID HARRINGTON.

15:05.639 --> 15:09.643
HE'S NOT ALLOWED VISITORS
UNLESS AUTHORIZED BY THE D. A.

15:09.643 --> 15:10.877
OR HIS ATTORNEY.

15:10.877 --> 15:12.445
I NEED TO SEE HIM NOW.

15:12.445 --> 15:13.947
YOU'RE NOT ON THE LIST SIR.

15:13.947 --> 15:16.182
NOT BY THE D. A.
AND NOT BY HIS ATTORNEY.

15:16.182 --> 15:17.450
DAMN IT!

15:22.589 --> 15:24.024
VERONICA:
Hi, leave a message.

15:24.024 --> 15:25.291
VERONICA, ANSWER YOUR PHONE!

15:31.397 --> 15:34.701
D.A. JENNIFER SALLISON
SENT OVER THESE DOCUMENTS

15:34.701 --> 15:37.170
AND TOLD ME THAT I HAD
TO SIGN OFF ON THE MONEY.

15:37.170 --> 15:40.340
SHE GAVE $12 MILLION
TO WYATT?

15:40.974 --> 15:42.275
YES.

15:43.510 --> 15:45.011
WHERE IS HE?
I DON'T KNOW.

15:46.813 --> 15:48.048
OH, MY GOD.

15:48.048 --> 15:50.216
HE MOVED THE MONEY
TO AN OFFSHORE ACCOUNT.

15:50.216 --> 15:51.251
AN OFFSHORE ACCOUNT?

15:55.556 --> 15:57.691
DID SHE REALLY DO THIS?

15:58.424 --> 15:59.926
I TRIED TO CALL YOU.

15:59.926 --> 16:01.434
I WAS IN JAIL, LLOYD.

16:01.434 --> 16:02.969
I'M SO SORRY.

16:04.304 --> 16:06.072
WHAT ELSE, LLOYD?

16:06.072 --> 16:08.341
WELL, WE NEED TO MOVE SOME MONEY
INTO THIS ACCOUNT.

16:09.175 --> 16:10.577
WHY?

16:10.577 --> 16:13.313
THE $7.4 MILLION THAT YOUR
HUSBAND TOOK OUT ‐‐

16:13.313 --> 16:14.314
YES.

16:14.314 --> 16:16.082
WENT TO
THE CANDY CANE COMPANY,

16:16.082 --> 16:18.218
BUT IT WAS ALLOCATED
FOR TAXES,

16:18.218 --> 16:19.586
AND NOW THE BILL IS DUE.

16:19.586 --> 16:21.722
WHAT THE HELL IS
THE CANDY CANE COMPANY?

16:21.722 --> 16:23.089
I THOUGHT THE SAME THING.

16:23.089 --> 16:24.625
IT'S OWNED BY CANDACE YOUNG.

16:33.499 --> 16:34.768
LLOYD.

16:36.002 --> 16:38.905
MOVE $8 MILLION
INTO THAT ACCOUNT, PLEASE.

16:38.905 --> 16:40.440
OKAY.

16:40.440 --> 16:42.743
YOUR OTHER ATTORNEY,
RICHARD, CALLED ALSO.

16:42.743 --> 16:43.710
AND?

16:43.710 --> 16:45.478
HE WAS TALKING
TO YOUR HUSBAND

16:45.478 --> 16:47.848
AND HE THINKS THAT
WE SHOULD MOVE $30 MILLION

16:47.848 --> 16:49.282
INTO THE BE WELL TRUST.

16:49.282 --> 16:50.183
WHAT FOR?

16:50.183 --> 16:51.618
IN CASE
THERE'S A LAWSUIT.

16:51.618 --> 16:53.520
THERE WILL NOT
BE A LAWSUIT.

16:53.520 --> 16:55.355
WELL, WE SHOULD
JUST IN CASE.

16:57.524 --> 16:58.992
DO IT.

16:58.992 --> 17:00.266
OKAY.

17:00.867 --> 17:02.268
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE?

17:02.268 --> 17:06.072
JUST THAT I'M SO VERY SORRY
ABOUT ALL THIS.

17:07.140 --> 17:08.408
LLOYD.

17:09.109 --> 17:10.143
STOP SWEATING.

17:10.877 --> 17:12.178
AND DON'T WORRY.

17:12.779 --> 17:14.548
I'M NOT TAKING MY MONEY
OUT OF YOUR BANK.

17:14.548 --> 17:15.982
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:15.982 --> 17:17.150
OKAY?

17:17.150 --> 17:18.451
I'VE GOT TO GET BACK
TO THE BANK.

17:19.319 --> 17:20.587
OKAY.
THANK YOU.

17:24.090 --> 17:25.759
HANNA.

17:25.759 --> 17:27.961
I'VE BEEN THROUGH
EVERY CUSHION,

17:27.961 --> 17:29.830
EVERY POCKET,
EVERY PURSE,

17:29.830 --> 17:34.134
AND I CAME UP WITH
ABOUT $987 AND SOME CHANGE.

17:34.134 --> 17:36.302
YOU STILL OWE ME $611.

17:36.302 --> 17:38.505
AND I'M GONNA COME BACK
AT THE FIRST OF THE MONTH

17:38.505 --> 17:39.506
AND GET IT.

17:39.506 --> 17:41.842
YOU CAN'T LEAVE.
I AM NOT YOUR SLAVE!

17:43.209 --> 17:45.178
THAT IS NOT THE WAY
I MEANT IT AND YOU KNOW IT.

17:45.178 --> 17:47.113
THAT SURE TO HELL
IS HOW YOU'RE TREATING ME.

17:48.515 --> 17:50.050
I CAN'T MAKE IT
WITHOUT YOU, HANNA.

17:50.050 --> 17:51.084
I WON'T!

17:51.084 --> 17:52.953
SO YOU HOLD A DOLLAR
OVER MY HEAD?

17:52.953 --> 17:54.755
NO, MA'AM.
NO, MA'AM.

17:55.756 --> 17:59.526
HERE.
TAKE MY RINGS.

18:01.134 --> 18:03.369
TAKE IT.
TAKE IT ALL.

18:03.870 --> 18:05.305
TAKE ALL THIS MONEY.
TAKE IT!

18:05.305 --> 18:06.740
I DON'T WANT THAT!

18:07.774 --> 18:10.210
I DON'T WANT NOTHING OTHER
THAN WHAT'S OWED ME.

18:10.210 --> 18:11.477
HANNA, PLEASE.

18:13.213 --> 18:14.715
PLEASE WHAT?

18:14.715 --> 18:17.350
THERE HAS NEVER BEEN ANYONE
WHO CARED FOR ME EVER.

18:19.953 --> 18:23.023
NOT MY HUSBAND,
NOT MY CHILDREN.

18:25.125 --> 18:26.426
NOT EVEN MY MOTHER.

18:28.461 --> 18:32.398
IF YOU WALK OUT THAT DOOR,
I AM LOST.

18:33.667 --> 18:35.235
YOU ALREADY LOST.

18:38.038 --> 18:39.640
WHAT CAN I GIVE YOU HERE?

18:39.640 --> 18:41.742
WHAT CAN I GIVE YOU
TO MAKE YOU STAY?

18:42.475 --> 18:45.145
[ SCOFFS ]

18:45.145 --> 18:48.982
THAT'S THE PROBLEM
WITH THE RICH.

18:48.982 --> 18:52.218
YOU ABLE TO BUY ANYTHING
YOU WANT,

18:52.218 --> 18:54.721
BUT YOU HAVE TO BEG
FOR WHAT YOU NEED.

18:56.857 --> 18:59.726
YOU DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
YOU CAN GIVE ME.

18:59.726 --> 19:01.034
I'M NOT FOR SALE.

19:03.504 --> 19:04.805
I KNOW.

19:06.740 --> 19:08.041
I KNOW.

19:09.743 --> 19:11.111
YOU'RE NOT YOUR DAUGHTER.

19:11.111 --> 19:12.378
NO, I'M NOT.

19:13.547 --> 19:15.215
BUT WHAT DOES SHE GOT
TO DO WITH THIS ANYWAY?

19:15.215 --> 19:18.885
[ SCOFFS ]

19:18.885 --> 19:24.390
$7.4 MILLION WIRE WAS SENT
TO THE CANDY CANE COMPANY

19:24.390 --> 19:26.292
BY JIM.

19:26.292 --> 19:28.494
OWNER ‐‐ CANDACE YOUNG.

19:29.663 --> 19:32.666
NOW, I KNOW THAT HE DID NOT
GIVE HER THAT MONEY WILLINGLY.

19:32.666 --> 19:33.934
SHE HAD TO HAVE
BLACKMAILED HIM.

19:35.836 --> 19:39.706
AND...

19:39.706 --> 19:41.307
THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY

19:41.307 --> 19:44.044
HAS GIVEN WYATT HIS
$12 MILLION INHERITANCE

19:44.044 --> 19:45.278
WITH NO GUARDIANSHIP.

19:49.349 --> 19:50.917
WYATT
IS GOING TO KILL HIMSELF

19:50.917 --> 19:53.019
WITH THAT AMOUNT
OF MONEY, HANNA,

19:53.019 --> 19:55.021
AND I CANNOT BURY
ANOTHER CHILD.

19:58.391 --> 19:59.660
PLEASE.

20:00.493 --> 20:02.035
I IMPLORE YOU.

20:03.704 --> 20:05.772
I AM BEGGING YOU.

20:05.772 --> 20:07.774
DO NOT LEAVE ME.

20:12.646 --> 20:15.448
I HAVE TO GO.

20:15.448 --> 20:18.985
IS THIS IT, HANNA?

20:18.985 --> 20:20.987
IS THIS IT?

20:26.059 --> 20:27.894
I GOT TO GO CHECK
ON MY GRANDSON.

20:31.565 --> 20:34.100
PLEASE.

20:35.068 --> 20:37.437
[ Crying ] PLEASE!

20:41.608 --> 20:44.645
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

20:58.625 --> 21:00.834
WANT TO TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED?

21:00.834 --> 21:03.436
THEY GOT ME
IN THE PAPER?

21:03.436 --> 21:07.373
THAT IS YOU, RIGHT?

21:07.373 --> 21:08.609
YEAH.

21:08.609 --> 21:10.744
AND THE HARRINGTON GUY
THAT CAME HERE, THAT'S HIS WIFE?

21:13.146 --> 21:15.181
YEAH.
HOW OLD IS SHE?

21:15.816 --> 21:17.618
OLD.

21:17.618 --> 21:20.621
WHAT'S GOING ON?

21:20.621 --> 21:22.122
[ SIGHS ]
OKAY.

21:22.122 --> 21:24.290
UH, I WAS MESSING AROUND
WITH HER.

21:26.059 --> 21:28.128
HE'S PISSED 'CAUSE
YOU'RE KNOCKING HER OFF,

21:28.128 --> 21:29.630
SO NOW HE'S MESSING
WITH OUR BUSINESS.

21:31.297 --> 21:32.833
YEAH.

21:32.833 --> 21:33.834
BENNY.

21:33.834 --> 21:34.901
LOOK, I DON'T ‐‐

21:34.901 --> 21:37.070
I DON'T KNOW
HOW HE DID THAT, ALL RIGHT?

21:37.070 --> 21:38.338
I KNOW HOW HE DID THAT.

21:38.338 --> 21:41.508
YOU KNOW, THESE FOLKS,
THEY'RE CONNECTED.

21:41.508 --> 21:43.610
YOU KNOW, BENNY, IT'S ‐‐
IT'S A SMALL TOWN.

21:43.610 --> 21:46.847
IT AIN'T KNOW BIG CITY,
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

21:46.847 --> 21:48.649
YOU CAN'T BE MESSING AROUND
WITH THESE PEOPLE LIKE THAT.

21:48.649 --> 21:49.950
I KNOW.

21:52.285 --> 21:54.187
SO, WHAT DOES HE WANT
TO GET OUR PHONES BACK ON?

21:56.122 --> 21:58.692
FOR ME
TO TELL HIM DETAILS.

21:58.692 --> 22:00.226
OKAY, SO TELL HIM.

22:00.226 --> 22:01.101
NO.

22:01.101 --> 22:02.302
NO?

22:02.302 --> 22:03.737
BRO, THAT'S FOR
HIS WIFE TO DO.

22:03.737 --> 22:05.171
LOOK, TELL THE MAN
WHAT HE WANTS TO KNOW

22:05.171 --> 22:07.140
SO HE CAN PUT OUR PHONES BACK ON
AND WE CAN GET BACK TO WORK.

22:07.140 --> 22:08.141
NO, I'M NOT DOING THAT,
ALL RIGHT?

22:08.141 --> 22:09.610
HE CAN TALK TO HIS WIFE.

22:09.610 --> 22:10.877
DAMN IT, BENNY, JUST TELL HIM
WHAT HE WANTS TO KNOW, BENNY,

22:10.877 --> 22:12.112
SO HE CAN PUT OUR PHONES
BACK ON

22:12.112 --> 22:14.480
AND WE CAN GET BACK TO WO‐‐
HEY.

22:14.480 --> 22:15.749
CANDACE.

22:17.283 --> 22:19.019
HOW'S IT GOING HERE?

22:19.019 --> 22:20.286
UH...

22:20.286 --> 22:21.487
IT'S GOOD.

22:21.487 --> 22:23.023
IT'S GOOD.
GOING GOOD.

22:23.023 --> 22:24.625
WHAT BRINGS YOU BY?

22:24.625 --> 22:26.159
I NEED TO TALK
TO MY BROTHER.

22:27.227 --> 22:29.162
WHAT'S UP?

22:29.162 --> 22:31.665
I'LL LET YOU GUYS TALK.

22:31.665 --> 22:33.066
THANKS, MITCH.
YEAH.

22:35.669 --> 22:37.571
SO, WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:37.571 --> 22:38.639
HAVE YOU SEEN WAR?

22:38.639 --> 22:39.806
YEAH.

22:39.806 --> 22:41.207
I TRIED TO GET HIM TO GO
INTO BUSINESS WITH ME,

22:41.207 --> 22:42.242
BUT HE WON'T.

22:44.277 --> 22:46.312
MAYBE THAT'S NOT
A GOOD IDEA.

22:46.312 --> 22:48.314
BUT YOU KNOW HE'S GOT
ALL THE CONNECTIONS.

22:48.314 --> 22:51.818
YEAH, BUT MAYBE GOING
INTO BUSINESS WITH HIM...

22:53.119 --> 22:55.922
MAYBE YOU SHOULDN'T GO
INTO BUSINESS WITH HIM.

22:55.922 --> 22:59.425
YEAH?

22:59.425 --> 23:00.801
WHY NOT?

23:03.069 --> 23:04.971
HEY, WAR.

23:04.971 --> 23:06.239
WHAT'S UP?

23:08.108 --> 23:09.142
HOW ARE YOU?

23:09.142 --> 23:09.976
I'M GOOD.

23:09.976 --> 23:11.277
GOOD, CANDACE.
HOW ARE YOU?

23:13.614 --> 23:15.348
GOOD. GOOD.

23:15.348 --> 23:16.382
PASSING THROUGH.

23:16.382 --> 23:17.884
YOU GOT A LEAK BACK THERE.

23:17.884 --> 23:19.252
YOU MIGHT WANT
TO GET THAT FIXED.

23:20.320 --> 23:22.055
APPRECIATE IT.

23:22.055 --> 23:24.324
COME ON, BABY.
GET A HUG.

23:29.930 --> 23:31.064
DON'T TRY IT, BITCH.

23:33.567 --> 23:35.869
OKAY.

23:35.869 --> 23:37.604
I'LL TALK TO YOU LATER?

23:39.305 --> 23:40.373
SURE.

23:42.943 --> 23:44.077
ALL RIGHT, B.

23:44.077 --> 23:45.045
ALL RIGHT.

23:50.917 --> 23:53.153
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:53.153 --> 23:54.655
BENNY,
WHAT IS HE DOING HERE.

23:54.655 --> 23:56.322
I TOLD YOU
I WAS TRYING TO GET HIM

23:56.322 --> 23:57.858
TO COME INTO
BUSINESS WITH ME.

23:57.858 --> 24:01.835
AND I TOLD YOU I DON'T THINK
IT'S A GOOD IDEA.

24:01.835 --> 24:03.069
HOW OFTEN IS HE HERE?

24:03.069 --> 24:04.505
HE DROPS BY ALL THE TIME.

24:04.505 --> 24:06.139
BENNY, THAT'S NOT GOOD.

24:06.139 --> 24:09.009
LOOK, I NEED ALL THE HELP
I CAN GET.

24:09.009 --> 24:10.276
WELL...

24:11.144 --> 24:12.445
...I DID.

24:13.914 --> 24:15.215
IS EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?

24:17.317 --> 24:18.585
I GOT IT.

24:20.453 --> 24:22.255
WHAT'S GOING ON?

24:22.255 --> 24:23.356
NOTHING.

24:23.356 --> 24:24.625
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU?

24:25.759 --> 24:27.493
HOW'S BUSINESS?

24:27.493 --> 24:28.795
IT'S GOOD.

24:32.966 --> 24:36.236
DID YOU THINK ABOUT
WHAT I SAID?

24:36.236 --> 24:37.838
WHAT?

24:37.838 --> 24:39.105
THE LAWSUIT.

24:40.941 --> 24:42.208
YEAH.

24:43.544 --> 24:44.845
AND?

24:45.445 --> 24:47.814
CANDACE, I'M ‐‐
I'M GOOD.

24:47.814 --> 24:49.783
THEY PAID
FOR MY HOSPITAL BILLS,

24:49.783 --> 24:52.085
I GOT THIS PLACE NOW.

24:52.085 --> 24:54.220
IT'S ALL GOOD.
LET'S JUST MOVE ON.

24:54.220 --> 24:56.122
BENNY,
YOU DESERVE THE MONEY.

24:56.122 --> 24:57.524
I SPOKE TO A FEW LAWYERS,

24:57.524 --> 24:59.993
AND I FOUND A REALLY
GOOD ONE WHO ‐‐

24:59.993 --> 25:01.467
WHO WILL SEE US.

25:01.467 --> 25:04.004
CANDACE. NO.

25:04.004 --> 25:09.009
HE SAID THAT YOU CAN GET,
LIKE, $10 MILLION.

25:09.009 --> 25:11.011
FOR REAL?
YES.

25:11.011 --> 25:12.879
THE CRYERS ARE LOADED.

25:16.750 --> 25:19.319
NO, I'M GONNA
MAKE THIS MYSELF.

25:19.319 --> 25:21.755
SO, YOU'VE BEEN TALKING
TO YOUR MOTHER.

25:21.755 --> 25:24.490
NO, I HAVEN'T BEEN TALKING
TO HER.

25:24.490 --> 25:26.026
WHY NOT?

25:26.026 --> 25:27.528
NO!

25:27.528 --> 25:29.530
BENNY, PLEASE.

25:29.530 --> 25:31.632
LIKE, WHY IS THIS SO IMPORTANT
TO YOU ANYWAY?

25:33.199 --> 25:34.735
THERE'S SOMETHING
I HAVE TO HANDLE.

25:34.735 --> 25:36.169
OH.

25:36.169 --> 25:37.437
WHAT NOW?

25:39.940 --> 25:41.441
I MAY NEED TO MORTGAGE
MY HOUSE.

25:43.376 --> 25:44.645
WHAT?

25:45.512 --> 25:46.780
YEAH.

25:48.348 --> 25:49.650
CANDACE.

25:50.984 --> 25:52.252
AND THIS PLACE.

25:53.654 --> 25:54.955
WHAT?

25:56.757 --> 25:57.758
AND YOUR HOUSE.

25:57.758 --> 26:00.967
[ SCOFFS ]

26:00.967 --> 26:02.402
NO WAY.

26:02.402 --> 26:04.037
I'LL PAY THE BILLS.

26:04.037 --> 26:05.772
YOU'VE LOST YOUR MIND.

26:05.772 --> 26:07.040
BENNY.

26:09.409 --> 26:10.677
WHAT KIND OF PROBLEM?

26:12.913 --> 26:14.480
THERE'S JUST SOMETHING
I NEED TO HANDLE.

26:14.480 --> 26:16.683
YOU KNOW WHAT, THAT'S IT.
GET OUT OF HERE.

26:16.683 --> 26:17.918
BENNY.
GET OUT.

26:18.552 --> 26:20.253
GET OUT NOW.
BENNY.

26:20.253 --> 26:21.855
ALL RIGHT,
FORGET I ASKED.

26:21.855 --> 26:23.323
WELL, YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT
I'M GONNA FORGET YOU ASKED,

26:23.323 --> 26:24.925
'CAUSE YOU LOST YOUR MIND.

26:24.925 --> 26:26.426
I MEAN,
DID WE FORGET WHAT, UH,

26:26.426 --> 26:28.962
WHAT HAPPENED
TO MOMMY'S HOUSE?

26:28.962 --> 26:31.231
I KNOW. I KNOW.

26:31.231 --> 26:33.567
AND WHAT DO YOU NEED
WITH THAT KIND OF MONEY ANYWAY?

26:33.567 --> 26:35.368
HMM?

26:35.368 --> 26:37.671
YOU IN TROUBLE?

26:37.671 --> 26:40.106
ARE YOU IN TROUBLE?
ANSWER ME.

26:40.106 --> 26:41.508
WHO IS IT?!

26:41.508 --> 26:42.609
CANDACE,
WHO IS IT?!

26:42.609 --> 26:43.910
I'LL KILL HIM!

26:44.978 --> 26:46.279
WHO IS IT?

26:47.313 --> 26:50.150
IS IT WHAT YOU DID
TO GET THIS PLACE? HMM?

26:50.150 --> 26:51.417
IS IT?!

26:55.121 --> 26:56.389
I'M NOT IN TROUBLE.

26:57.958 --> 26:59.259
CANDACE, WHO IS IT?

27:01.367 --> 27:03.003
IT WAS A BUSINESS DEAL.

27:03.003 --> 27:06.907
IT WAS A BUSINESS OPPORTUNITY
THAT I WILL PASS ON.

27:06.907 --> 27:08.842
IT'S OKAY.
OKAY?

27:08.842 --> 27:10.210
THAT'S ALL IT WAS.

27:10.210 --> 27:11.678
YEAH.
I'LL MISS IT.

27:11.678 --> 27:14.014
YEAH, WELL, YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT
YOU'RE GONNA MISS IT.

27:14.014 --> 27:15.215
AND LET ME
TELL YOU SOMETHING,

27:15.215 --> 27:18.251
YOU DON'T ASK ME
THAT AGAIN, YOU HEAR ME?

27:18.251 --> 27:19.786
OKAY.

27:19.786 --> 27:22.556
CA ‐‐ CALM DOWN.
DON'T!

27:22.556 --> 27:25.659
OKAY,
I'M SORRY I ASKED.

27:25.659 --> 27:26.927
YOU RIGHT ABOUT THAT.

27:30.163 --> 27:33.466
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:33.466 --> 27:34.467
WOW.

27:34.467 --> 27:35.569
WOW WHAT?
THAT AIN'T FUNNY.

27:35.569 --> 27:37.470
I WAS ‐‐
I WAS KIDDING.

27:37.470 --> 27:38.739
WELL, DON'T PLAY
LIKE THAT.

27:41.107 --> 27:42.408
OKAY.

27:42.408 --> 27:44.044
GOSH.

27:44.044 --> 27:46.079
WILL YOU AT LEAST
MEET WITH THE LAWYER?

27:47.714 --> 27:48.982
CANDACE.

27:50.283 --> 27:51.718
BENNY, PLEASE.

27:51.718 --> 27:54.420
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT
$10 MILLION.

27:56.790 --> 27:58.592
YOU MAY NOT EVEN
HAVE TO SUE.

28:00.393 --> 28:02.002
YOU'LL PROBABLY
GET A SETTLEMENT.

28:02.002 --> 28:03.570
I‐I‐I KNOW IT.

28:05.038 --> 28:07.440
YOU DON'T EVEN
HAVE TO GO TO COURT.

28:07.440 --> 28:10.644
MAMA WON'T KNOW IF THAT'S WHAT
YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT, BENNY.

28:10.644 --> 28:12.813
YOU HAVE TO AT LEAST
MEET THE LAWYERS.

28:12.813 --> 28:16.116
PLEASE.

28:16.116 --> 28:17.483
PLEASE?
[ SIGHS ]

28:17.483 --> 28:20.120
ALL RIGHT,
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

28:20.120 --> 28:21.955
OKAY.

28:21.955 --> 28:23.890
THINK ABOUT IT
WHILE YOU TAKE ME TO LUNCH.

28:23.890 --> 28:28.261
[ LAUGHS ]
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

28:28.261 --> 28:30.063
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

28:30.063 --> 28:31.331
HELLO?

28:31.331 --> 28:33.466
MAN: I have to go to
the dealership to show I. D.

28:33.466 --> 28:34.768
I'll be right back.

28:34.768 --> 28:37.170
OKAY.
UM, JUST LOCK THE DOOR.

28:37.170 --> 28:38.471
Okay.

28:41.041 --> 28:42.308
COME ON, BENNY.

28:43.877 --> 28:45.111
YOU'RE GONNA TAKE ME
TO LUNCH.

28:53.386 --> 28:54.988
YOU'RE DOING
TOO MUCH.

28:54.988 --> 28:55.956
SHUT UP.

28:55.956 --> 28:57.558
OKAY.

28:57.558 --> 28:58.959
I TOLD YOU.

28:58.959 --> 29:00.360
YOU BITCH.

29:00.360 --> 29:02.068
I TOLD YOU.

29:02.068 --> 29:04.571
[ SIGHS ]

29:19.285 --> 29:21.321
[ DOOR BUZZES ]

29:24.891 --> 29:25.892
HI.

29:25.892 --> 29:27.127
HI.

29:27.861 --> 29:29.162
YOU LOOK NICE.

29:29.996 --> 29:31.264
DON'T.

29:31.798 --> 29:33.299
WHAT?
DON'T BE NICE.

29:33.299 --> 29:35.869
I NEED YOU TO BE THE ASS
THAT YOU ALWAYS ARE.

29:35.869 --> 29:38.304
'CAUSE I AM NOT IN THE MOOD
FOR A NICE JIM RIGHT NOW,

29:38.304 --> 29:40.073
BECAUSE THEN I'LL KNOW
YOU'RE WORRIED,

29:40.073 --> 29:41.908
AND I'M ALREADY HAVING
THE DAY FROM HELL.

29:43.577 --> 29:44.845
I'M NOT WORRIED,
KATHERYN.

29:44.845 --> 29:46.046
WELL, GOOD,
'CAUSE I AM.

29:46.046 --> 29:47.313
DON'T BE.

29:48.314 --> 29:50.050
DID LLOYD CALL YOU?
YES.

29:50.050 --> 29:51.785
HE TOLD YOU THERE'S LIKELY
TO BE A LAWSUIT?

29:51.785 --> 29:53.654
YES.
HAS ONE BEEN FILED?

29:53.654 --> 29:55.188
NO, BUT AS
A FORMER LITIGATOR,

29:55.188 --> 29:57.724
I CAN ALREADY SMELL
THE AMBULANCE CHASERS LINING UP.

29:59.926 --> 30:02.035
DID YOU HAPPEN TO REMEMBER ‐‐
YES, I HAD FUNDS MOVED.

30:02.035 --> 30:04.037
GOOD.
THANK YOU.

30:07.140 --> 30:08.408
HANNA QUIT.

30:09.375 --> 30:10.711
HMM.

30:10.711 --> 30:12.579
FIRST STEP
IN THE LAWSUIT.

30:12.579 --> 30:13.714
I'M NOT SO SURE.

30:13.714 --> 30:15.949
I THINK YOU'RE WRONG.

30:15.949 --> 30:19.953
I'M NOT WRONG, KATHERYN.

30:19.953 --> 30:21.588
DID LLOYD TELL YOU
ABOUT WYATT?

30:23.924 --> 30:25.225
WHAT ABOUT WYATT?

30:26.126 --> 30:27.393
FIGURES.

30:28.028 --> 30:30.931
KNEW HE WOULD LEAVE IT
TO ME TO TELL YOU.

30:30.931 --> 30:33.634
LEAVE IT TO YOU
TO TELL ME WHAT?

30:33.634 --> 30:36.302
JENNIFER SALLISON
HAD HIS INHERITANCE RELEASED.

30:38.338 --> 30:39.806
SHE DID WHAT?

30:39.806 --> 30:41.074
YES.

30:42.042 --> 30:42.943
WHERE IS HE?

30:42.943 --> 30:43.910
I DON'T KNOW.

30:43.910 --> 30:45.378
WHERE IS HE, KATHERYN?

30:45.378 --> 30:46.847
YOU HAVE TO FIND HIM.
I DON'T KNOW!

30:46.847 --> 30:48.615
YOU KNOW THIS MONEY
IS GONNA DESTROY OUR SON.

30:48.615 --> 30:49.750
YOU THINK?!

30:50.951 --> 30:52.285
I NEED TO GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE.

30:52.285 --> 30:54.087
WELL, MAYBE IF YOU WOULD STOP
CALLING JUDGES ASSES,

30:54.087 --> 30:55.656
THAT WOULD HAPPEN.
THOSE SONS OF BITCHES

30:55.656 --> 30:57.624
DON'T DESERVE TO BE ON THE
BENCH IN THE FIRST PLACE.

30:57.624 --> 30:59.425
WELL, THAT MAY BE TRUE,
BUT YOU CAN'T SAY THAT!

30:59.425 --> 31:00.661
FIND HIM, KATHERYN!
FIND HIM.

31:00.661 --> 31:01.968
I WILL, JIM.
I WILL.

31:01.968 --> 31:04.004
AND WHEN YOU SEE SALLISON,
I WANT YOU TO MAKE SURE

31:04.004 --> 31:04.971
AND RIP HER A NEW ONE.

31:04.971 --> 31:06.439
JIM.
MAKE SURE THAT SHE IS REMINDED

31:06.439 --> 31:09.275
WHY YOUR NAME
IS KATHERYN HARDGRAVE‐CRYER.

31:09.275 --> 31:11.177
DON'T WORRY.

31:11.177 --> 31:13.213
[ DOOR BUZZES ]

31:21.487 --> 31:23.757
WYATT:
Hi, you've reached Wyatt Cryer.
Leave a message after the beep.

31:23.757 --> 31:25.626
[ VOICEMAIL BEEPS ]
HE'S NOT ANSWERING.

31:27.127 --> 31:29.696
GET A WARRANT AND TRACK HIS NAME
FOR ME, PLEASE.

31:29.696 --> 31:31.497
THANK YOU.

31:31.497 --> 31:34.100
WYATT CRYER,
WHERE ARE YOU?

31:35.035 --> 31:36.269
WHERE'S VERONICA?

31:36.803 --> 31:38.171
HI TO YOU, TOO.

31:38.171 --> 31:39.773
HI. WHERE IS VERONICA?

31:39.773 --> 31:41.842
YOU CAN'T JUST COME BARGING
INTO MY OFFICE ‐‐

31:41.842 --> 31:43.176
JENNIFER!

31:43.176 --> 31:45.278
WHERE IS MY WIFE?

31:45.278 --> 31:46.780
I DON'T KNOW.

31:46.780 --> 31:48.448
I NEED AN ADDRESS.

31:48.448 --> 31:50.684
WHAT?
DID SHE LEAVE HER HOME ADDRESS?

31:50.684 --> 31:53.086
HOW DO YOU NOT KNOW YOUR WIFE'S
HOME ADDRESS?

31:53.086 --> 31:56.222
JENNIFER, DID SHE LEAVE
A HOME ADDRESS?

31:56.222 --> 31:57.524
NO.

31:58.358 --> 32:01.367
ANSWER ME!
LET GO.

32:01.367 --> 32:03.303
I NEED TO SEE JIM.

32:03.303 --> 32:05.338
YOU NEED TO SEE
MAGGIE DAY.

32:06.540 --> 32:08.542
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

32:08.542 --> 32:11.578
I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON
BETWEEN THE TWO OF YOU.

32:11.578 --> 32:13.580
I AM NOT DOING THIS
WITH YOU RIGHT NOW.

32:13.580 --> 32:15.448
YOU HAVE TIME
FOR HER BUT NOT FOR ME, RIGHT?

32:15.448 --> 32:17.483
I NEED TO SEE JIM NOW!

32:17.483 --> 32:19.285
I SAID LET GO!

32:24.124 --> 32:25.425
PLEASE.

32:27.127 --> 32:28.328
JENNIFER, LOOK AT ME.

32:32.398 --> 32:33.667
PLEASE.

32:37.337 --> 32:39.372
WHAT'S GOING ON?

32:39.372 --> 32:42.709
I NEED TO SEE JIM,
PLEASE.

32:43.944 --> 32:45.245
OKAY, FIVE MINUTES.

32:46.046 --> 32:47.313
THANK YOU.

32:55.589 --> 32:57.423
HI, THIS IS
JENNIFER SALLISON.

32:57.423 --> 33:01.802
UM, I HAVE DAVID HARRINGTON
COMING DOWN TO SEE JIM CRYER.

33:03.937 --> 33:05.205
OKAY, OKAY, THANK YOU.

33:15.749 --> 33:17.417
Lawyer:
THIS IS AN EASY CASE TO WIN.

33:17.417 --> 33:18.451
YOU SEE, BENNY?

33:18.451 --> 33:20.286
AND WITH THEM TRYING
TO COVER IT UP...

33:22.455 --> 33:23.524
I DON'T KNOW.

33:23.524 --> 33:26.259
YOU SHOULD CONSIDER IT.

33:26.259 --> 33:27.427
LOOK, I DON'T ‐‐

33:27.427 --> 33:30.797
DON'T YOU THINK THEY WOULD
SETTLE TO AVOID A TRIAL?

33:30.797 --> 33:33.199
YEAH.
YEAH, MOST PEOPLE WOULD.

33:33.199 --> 33:35.035
SETTLEMENT'S A REAL
POSSIBILITY HERE.

33:35.035 --> 33:36.670
ESPECIALLY IF WE CAN GET
THE GRANDFATHER AND THE MOTHER

33:36.670 --> 33:37.738
OF THE LITTLE GIRL.

33:37.738 --> 33:39.640
THE GRANDFATHER
AND THE MOTHER TO JOIN?

33:39.640 --> 33:41.975
MM‐HMM.
WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO FIND HIM.

33:41.975 --> 33:43.076
WE KNOW THEM.

33:43.076 --> 33:45.145
NO, WE DON'T.
YES, WE DO.

33:46.680 --> 33:48.148
NO, WE DON'T.

33:48.148 --> 33:49.950
I WILL REACH OUT
TO THEM.

33:49.950 --> 33:51.752
THAT WOULD BE GREAT.

33:51.752 --> 33:52.853
I DON'T LIKE THAT DUDE.

33:52.853 --> 33:54.621
CALL HIM.

33:54.621 --> 33:56.489
IF THE TWO OF YOU JOIN TOGETHER,
IT WOULD JUST MAKE THE CASE

33:56.489 --> 33:57.958
THAT MUCH EASIER.

33:57.958 --> 33:59.259
NO.

33:59.259 --> 34:01.434
I WILL CALL HIM TO SEE
IF HE WILL MEET ME AT MY HOUSE.

34:01.434 --> 34:02.903
I'M SURE
I CAN GET HIM TO JOIN US.

34:03.704 --> 34:06.106
NOW, HOLD ON, HOLD ON.
LIKE, I DIDN'T ‐‐

34:06.106 --> 34:07.473
I DIDN'T EVEN SAY YES
TO THIS.

34:07.473 --> 34:08.509
HE WILL.

34:08.509 --> 34:10.511
NO.
NO, I'M NOT.

34:10.511 --> 34:12.646
MY MONEY
IS ON YOUR SISTER.

34:12.646 --> 34:13.947
SHE CAN BE
VERY PERSUASIVE.

34:16.249 --> 34:18.284
YOU KNOW,
YOU COULD BE A LAWYER.

34:18.284 --> 34:19.653
I'M IN LAW SCHOOL.

34:19.653 --> 34:21.522
IS THAT SO?
YEAH.

34:21.522 --> 34:23.624
YOU SHOULD COME SEE ME
WHEN YOU GRADUATE.

34:23.624 --> 34:26.292
REALLY?
YEAH.

34:26.292 --> 34:27.628
OKAY.

34:27.628 --> 34:31.131
AND IF YOU CAN MAKE THIS HAPPEN,
DEFINITELY COME SEE ME.

34:32.432 --> 34:33.700
I'LL DO THAT.

34:34.300 --> 34:36.703
SO, LOOK,
I'M DUE IN COURT.

34:36.703 --> 34:38.805
IF YOU GET THE GRANDFATHER
TO COME IN, LET'S MEET.

34:38.805 --> 34:41.542
OKAY. MY HOUSE.
I'LL CALL YOU.

34:41.542 --> 34:43.409
OKAY, THANKS.
MY SECRETARY WILL SHOW YOU OUT.

34:43.409 --> 34:44.310
THANK YOU.

34:44.310 --> 34:46.379
I'M NOT DEALING WITH
THAT DUDE.

34:46.379 --> 34:48.515
THIS IS ABOUT MILLIONS
OF DOLLARS.

34:48.515 --> 34:50.617
YES, YOU ARE.

34:57.791 --> 34:58.892
MS. YOUNG?

34:58.892 --> 35:00.293
HI.
HI.

35:00.293 --> 35:01.935
HOW IS HE?
HE'S GREAT.

35:01.935 --> 35:03.937
WHERE IS HE?
HE'S IN HIS ROOM.

35:03.937 --> 35:05.639
WHICH WAY IS THAT?

35:05.639 --> 35:07.440
I'M SORRY,
BUT YOU CAN'T SEE HIM.

35:07.440 --> 35:08.675
WHAT?
NO, MA'AM.

35:08.675 --> 35:10.443
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

35:10.443 --> 35:12.478
YOU ‐‐ YOU NEED TO TALK
TO CHILD WELFARE.

35:12.478 --> 35:13.747
WELL, WHERE ARE THEY?

35:14.748 --> 35:16.382
THEY WERE JUST HERE.

35:16.382 --> 35:17.751
MISS DELONG?

35:17.751 --> 35:20.353
YES. YOU KNOW HER?
YES, I DO.

35:20.353 --> 35:21.522
HI.

35:21.522 --> 35:24.024
YOU SAID I HAD UNTIL MONDAY
AT 3:00.

35:24.024 --> 35:26.059
YES, WELL,
WE SIDED WITH HIS MOTHER.

35:27.427 --> 35:28.829
MISS DELONG, PLEASE.

35:28.829 --> 35:31.297
NOW, YOU KNOW I'M THE BEST
CAREGIVER FOR THAT CHILD.

35:31.297 --> 35:32.899
YOU HAVE NOWHERE
FOR HIM TO LIVE.

35:32.899 --> 35:35.101
YEAH, BUT YOU CAN'T EVEN
VERIFY HER JOB.

35:35.101 --> 35:36.402
I'M SORRY.

35:37.037 --> 35:38.438
LOOK AT ME.

35:38.438 --> 35:39.940
WHAT?

35:39.940 --> 35:42.208
LOOK AT ME.
YES.

35:43.677 --> 35:45.311
SHE GOT TO YOU,
DIDN'T SHE?

35:45.311 --> 35:46.580
NO.

35:47.548 --> 35:48.815
LOOK AT ME.

35:50.617 --> 35:53.286
YOU CAN'T EVEN
LOOK ME IN MY EYES.

35:53.286 --> 35:54.788
WHAT DID SHE DO TO YOU?

35:56.790 --> 35:58.859
NOTHING.

35:58.859 --> 36:00.160
I'M SORRY.

36:00.160 --> 36:02.102
I DID WHAT'S BEST
FOR YOUR GRANDSON.

36:03.069 --> 36:04.738
HOW DID YOU GET THAT BRUISE
ON YOUR...

36:04.738 --> 36:05.806
I'M FINE.

36:07.373 --> 36:08.675
WHAT DID SHE DO?

36:10.877 --> 36:12.145
I'M SORRY.

36:14.014 --> 36:15.281
DID SHE COME
AND GET HIM?

36:17.283 --> 36:18.552
NO, NOT YET.

36:19.185 --> 36:20.486
CAN I SEE HIM?

36:22.355 --> 36:23.456
I'M SORRY.

36:23.456 --> 36:25.125
PLEASE.

36:25.125 --> 36:26.426
NO, YOU CAN'T.

36:29.963 --> 36:31.331
WHEN SHE COMING
TO GET HIM?

36:32.232 --> 36:33.499
I'M NOT SURE.

36:35.435 --> 36:36.703
OKAY.

36:38.939 --> 36:40.206
OKAY.

36:42.208 --> 36:43.176
[ SCOFFS ]

36:43.176 --> 36:44.477
OKAY.

36:52.218 --> 36:54.821
SO, WHAT DID BENNY SAY?

36:54.821 --> 36:57.958
HE LOST IT WHEN I ASKED HIM
ABOUT THE MORTGAGE.

36:57.958 --> 36:59.259
CANDACE.

37:02.902 --> 37:05.639
I'LL LET YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU HAVE TO DO.

37:05.639 --> 37:06.940
ERICA.

37:08.107 --> 37:09.743
LOOK, I CAN GET
THE DOCUMENTS FORGED.

37:10.777 --> 37:12.278
THEY'LL LOOK
JUST LIKE HIS.

37:12.278 --> 37:13.813
ERICA.

37:13.813 --> 37:15.749
I CAN HAVE THEM
IN AN HOUR.

37:15.749 --> 37:17.984
I CAN'T.
TAKE THEM TO THE BANK.

37:17.984 --> 37:19.620
YOU HAVE
ALL THE APPRAISALS.

37:19.620 --> 37:22.288
BENNY WOULD KILL ME IF HE FOUND
OUT I MORTGAGED HIS HOUSE

37:22.288 --> 37:23.657
AND HIS BUSINESS.

37:23.657 --> 37:25.592
IT'S IN HIS NAME,
AND I‐I FORGE HIS NAME ‐‐

37:25.592 --> 37:27.894
HAVE YOU GOTTEN SOFT,
CANDACE?

37:29.295 --> 37:31.097
THAT'S MY BROTHER.

37:31.097 --> 37:32.666
HE'S THE ONLY ONE
WHO LOVES ME, ERICA.

37:32.666 --> 37:35.501
YEAH, BUT THIS IS WAR
YOU'RE DEALING WITH.

37:37.838 --> 37:40.807
I KNOW.

37:40.807 --> 37:42.976
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

37:42.976 --> 37:47.247
YOUR PHONE'S RINGING.

37:47.247 --> 37:50.150
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

37:50.150 --> 37:51.417
HI.

37:52.285 --> 37:53.453
THIS IS CANDACE YOUNG.

37:55.321 --> 37:56.623
IT'S HANNA'S DAUGHTER.

37:58.291 --> 38:00.527
I'M GUESSING
YOU HEARD ABOUT THE CASE

38:00.527 --> 38:02.769
WITH THE CRYERS
AND MY BROTHER.

38:05.238 --> 38:07.340
BENNY'S SUING THE CRYERS.

38:07.340 --> 38:09.109
WE'VE RETAINED THE BEST
LAWYER IN TOWN,

38:09.109 --> 38:12.278
AND WE WANT YOU
TO JOIN US.

38:12.278 --> 38:13.580
YEAH.

38:15.916 --> 38:17.818
NO, WE DIDN'T
TELL HER YET.

38:17.818 --> 38:19.285
SHE WORKS FOR THEM,

38:19.285 --> 38:21.021
SO IT'S A BIT
OF A CONFLICT OF INTEREST,

38:21.021 --> 38:22.756
BUT WE WILL, THOUGH.

38:24.791 --> 38:26.960
YEAH, IT'S LEGIT.

38:26.960 --> 38:29.262
WE WON'T KEEP ANYTHING
FROM HER.

38:29.262 --> 38:31.264
CAN YOU COME TO MY HOUSE

38:31.264 --> 38:34.200
AND WE WILL FILL YOU
IN ON EVERYTHING LATER?

38:36.102 --> 38:37.403
THAT'S PERFECT.

38:37.403 --> 38:38.772
I'LL TEXT
YOU MY ADDRESS,

38:38.772 --> 38:41.508
AND THE ATTORNEY WILL BE THERE
TO EXPLAIN EVERYTHING

38:41.508 --> 38:42.809
TO YOU AND BENNY.

38:44.110 --> 38:45.378
SURE.

38:47.814 --> 38:49.650
WHO WAS THAT?
[ SIGHS ]

38:49.650 --> 38:51.451
THE GRANDFATHER
OF THE LITTLE GIRL.

38:53.053 --> 38:54.755
OKAY. SEE?

38:54.755 --> 38:56.489
YOU GET THE MORTGAGE
AND THEN ‐‐

38:56.489 --> 38:59.459
AND THEN JUST PAY IT OFF
WHEN THE SETTLEMENT COMES IN.

38:59.459 --> 39:01.067
THAT'S BENNY'S MONEY.

39:01.067 --> 39:02.435
YEAH, WELL, MAKE A DEAL

39:02.435 --> 39:04.771
WITH THE ATTORNEY
FOR MAKING THIS ALL HAPPEN.

39:05.305 --> 39:07.307
WE GET IN THE MIDDLE
OF IT.

39:07.307 --> 39:09.643
YOU NEED TO GET
THAT MORTGAGE, CANDACE.

39:09.643 --> 39:11.377
WHAT TIME IS IT?

39:11.377 --> 39:13.514
PICK UP MY SON.

39:13.514 --> 39:15.215
OKAY.

39:15.215 --> 39:16.316
I'M GONNA WORK ON
THE DEEDS.

39:16.316 --> 39:17.551
ERICA.

39:17.551 --> 39:18.852
YOU DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

39:31.532 --> 39:33.934
[ DOOR OPENS ]

39:33.934 --> 39:36.870
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

40:09.876 --> 40:11.111
DIAL MAGGIE DAY.

40:13.146 --> 40:15.982
MAGGIE: Hello?
MAGGIE.

40:15.982 --> 40:18.018
Mrs. Harrington.

40:18.018 --> 40:20.587
I KNOW YOU PLANTED
THE PICTURE.

40:20.587 --> 40:24.390
Yes, I did.

40:24.390 --> 40:26.793
THANK YOU.
Excuse me?

40:26.793 --> 40:29.896
YOU DID SOMETHING
I NEVER HAD THE STRENGTH TO DO.

40:31.364 --> 40:33.166
I KNEW
MY MARRIAGE WAS OVER,

40:33.166 --> 40:36.336
BUT I COULDN'T...

40:36.336 --> 40:37.838
I HAVE SOME THINGS

40:37.838 --> 40:40.607
THAT ARE TOO SENSITIVE
TO SHARE OVER THE PHONE.

40:40.607 --> 40:43.877
CAN YOU MEET ME AT, UH...

40:43.877 --> 40:45.145
MY HOUSE?

40:46.680 --> 40:48.982
I WILL TELL YOU
EVERYTHING.

40:48.982 --> 40:51.685
THERE'S SOME THINGS ABOUT DAVID
THAT YOU NEED TO KNOW.

40:54.187 --> 40:55.756
CAN YOU MEET ME IN A COUPLE
OF HOURS?

40:55.756 --> 40:58.592
I HAVE SOME ERRANDS
TO RUN.

40:58.592 --> 40:59.860
Sure.

41:01.027 --> 41:03.837
OKAY, SO I'LL TEXT YOU
WHEN I'M CLOSE.

41:03.837 --> 41:05.539
Okay.

41:05.539 --> 41:06.840
MAGGIE?

41:09.242 --> 41:10.844
THANK YOU.

41:10.844 --> 41:12.145
Bye.

41:15.782 --> 41:18.685
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

41:18.685 --> 41:21.588
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

41:27.661 --> 41:30.096
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:30.096 --> 41:31.698
JIM, WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

41:31.698 --> 41:33.433
IT'S TOO LATE.

41:33.433 --> 41:34.701
CALL IT OFF, JIM.

41:34.701 --> 41:36.903
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

41:36.903 --> 41:37.938
I NEED TO SEE YOUR SISTER.

41:37.938 --> 41:40.541
MOM ‐‐
MOVE!

41:40.541 --> 41:41.975
HANNA.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

41:41.975 --> 41:43.810
WE HAVEN'T TOLD HER.

41:43.810 --> 41:45.445
DON'T THROW ANYTHING
AT ME.

41:45.445 --> 41:49.750
BITCH, I WILL HAVE YOU MURDERED
IN THE STREETS.

41:49.750 --> 41:51.117
Man:
I found Veronica's house.

41:51.117 --> 41:52.352
DAVID:
What's the address?

41:52.352 --> 41:54.521
611 Westchester Lane.

41:54.521 --> 41:56.557
[ HEART BEATING ]
